Drop the real inbound RFP PDF in this directory, renamed to `rfp-inbound.pdf`.

Then ask your lead agent (Claude Desktop / Cursor / Claude Code):

    Read rfp-inbound.pdf from the local directory. Extract the text content,
    then use costate_write to save it as rfp-inbound.md in the workspace.

Your agent will use its native PDF reading + filesystem access to pull the
content, then write the markdown version to the workspace via `costate_write`.

This placeholder file can be deleted once the real RFP is in the workspace.
